W/A/S/D            -> Moving
Space              -> Jumping
LCTRL              -> Crouching
LSHIFT             -> Running
ALT                -> Toggle quiet mode
LCTRL 2x           -> Laying down
LSHIFT 2x          -> Emergency running
W + SPACE          -> Climbing up short objects
LSHIFT + W + SPACE -> Climbing up taller object or jump over short objects
TAB                -> Checking missions
Y                  -> Checking map
ESC                -> Open pause menu
